        header#home
            .header-content
                h1 BUSINESS  
                span.header-content__item-transform
                    span.header-content__item-list
                        span.header-content__item SOLUTIONS 
                        span.header-content__item TEMPLATES 
                        span.header-content__item SERVICES
                p Aria is a top consultancy company specializing in business growth using online marketing and conversion optimization tactics
                a.header-content__btn(href='#') DISCOVER
        .container.container-intro#intro
            .intro-left
                .intro-left__title INTRO
                h2 We Offer Some Of The Best Business Growth Services In Town
                p Launching a new company or developing the market position of an existing one can be quite an overwhelming processs at times.
                p.intro-left__text "Our mission here at Aira is to get you through those tough moments relying on our team's expertise in starting and growing companies."
                .intro-left__author Louise Donovan - CEO
            .intro-right
                img(src="images/intro-office.jpg", alt="intro")
        .container-service#service
            .container
                .container-service__title SERVICES
                h2 Choose The Service Package
                h2 That Suits Your Needs
                .container-service__item-list
                    .container-service__item
                        .container-service__item-content
                            img(src="images/services-1.jpg", alt="service")
                            h3 Off The Ground
                            p Perfect for fresh ideas or young startups, this package will help get the business off the ground
                            ul
                                li Environment and competition
                                li Designing the marketing plan
                            h4 Starting at 
                                strong $199
                        .container-service__btn-details DETAILS
                    .container-service__item
                        .container-service__item-content
                            img(src="images/services-2.jpg", alt="service")
                            h3 Accelerated Growth
                            p Use this service pack to give your company the necessary impulse to become an industry leader
                            ul
                                li Business strategy planning
                                li Taking the planned actions
                            h4 Starting at 
                                strong $299
                        .container-service__btn-details DETAILS
                    .container-service__item
                        .container-service__item-content
                            img(src="images/services-3.jpg", alt="service")
                            h3 Market Domination
                            p You already are a reference point in your industry now you need to learn about acquisitions
                            ul
                                li Maintaining the leader status
                                li Acquisitions the right way
                            h4 Starting at 
                                strong $199
                        .container-service__btn-details DETAILS
