        .container.container-about#about
            .container-about__left
                img(src="images/about.jpg", alt="intro")
            .container-about__right
                .container-about__right-title ABOUT
                h2 We're Passionate About Delivering Growth Services
                p Our goal is to provide the right business growth services at the appropriate time so companies can benefit from the created momentum and thrive for a long period of time
